cull-less-leaves.title: Cull Less Leaves
cull-less-leaves.option.depth.tooltip:
Amount of layers of leaves before the inside of the leaves is culled.
1 = Fastest but least good-looking.
2 = Recommended.
4 = Slowest but most good-looking.
cull-less-leaves.option.random_rejection: Reject a percentage of inner-layer leaves inside of the accepted depth range randomly.
cull-less-leaves.option.fast_mangrove_ro: Does a depth-1 cull on mangrove roots, any more is useless as roots generate in single layers. This doesn't do much.
